# Netlify/Vercel Redirects for LLM Works Domain Migration
# From aegis-ai.com to llmworks.dev

# Legacy domain redirects (when old domain is available)
https://aegis-ai.com/* https://llmworks.dev/:splat 301!
http://aegis-ai.com/* https://llmworks.dev/:splat 301!

# Subdomain redirects
https://www.aegis-ai.com/* https://llmworks.dev/:splat 301!
https://app.aegis-ai.com/* https://llmworks.dev/:splat 301!

# Common old paths to new structure
/aegis/* /arena/:splat 301
/aegis-ai/* /:splat 301
/platform/* /:splat 301

# API endpoint redirects (if applicable)
/api/v1/aegis/* /api/v1/:splat 301

# Documentation redirects  
/docs/aegis/* /docs/:splat 301

